      "side": 1,
      "message": "chatted. I didn\u0027t realize that with my suggestion is lossy: we loose info that a segment of chunks belong to a same line and must be processed in a certain way if the whole line matches a prefix.\n\ni guess a generic implementation could split description by lines and determine a list of linkifiers for each line (e.g. no match -\u003e just URL linkfier. A bug line -\u003e URL linkified and bug linkifier) and process each line individually. But this is probably an overkill for what we have today, so this code LGTM",
